{
  "stem": "13623.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "We see the Germans go over to them, and they hand them their guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "There were British soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "We did not know the difference in uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "We knew that-- we knew they were not German uniforms, but we didn't know-- we did not know they were German, or they were British.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "As soon as it set in, in our minds, what is happening, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I saw the first lynching in my life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "A kapo, who was a real, real bad man, who didn't treat his fellow prisoners right, was the first man that I've seen-- first of a few, that I've seen being lynched.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "They actually beat him to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "Nobody stopped anybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It happened to a couple of-- few people like this that I've seen happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all-- we were all standing outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all-- we were just liberated, but we didn't comprehend what was happening at-- to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as soon as we realized what was happening, the other prisoners took it out on the-- on the-- on the prisoners that were-- that were-- that didn't behave to us the way they should have.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now we're liberated, but for some reason, the British army didn't let us-- we were still in the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We still cannot get out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The army is continuing because the war is not over yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They are continuing on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just a few soldiers are left with the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- Hungary was an ally of Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a Hungarian military detachment close by, apparently.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To this day, I don't understand why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These Hungarians, they were, in many cases, worse to us than the Germans when we were in the-- we were in the ghetto and before.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
